sql:
SELECT AVG(salary_amount) AS average_salary
FROM salary_history
WHERE bonus_amount > 5000;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT employee_id) AS unique_employees_with_reviews_last_year
FROM performance_reviews
WHERE review_date BETWEEN DATE('now', '-1 year') AND DATE('now');

external_knowledge:
- 'More than a handful' refers to more than 5 completions;
- The programs are considered popular if they are completed by more than five employees;
- The count of completions is sorted from the most completed to the least.
